{"tid":1278419,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"［求解讀］台灣郵局7月起停收「港、歐及人民幣」只限「美元」匯入","createTime":"2019-07-02T12:32:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T16:10:54.000Z","uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"95fd10f2fc261d0080672ce22dc255be0b59427f","tid":1278419,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:32:21.000Z","msg":"記者謝承恩／台北報導<br />\n<br />\n中華郵政公司自108年7月1日起，外匯匯款業務合作銀行由永豐銀行變更為美國紐約梅隆銀行，合作銀行扣收費用將配合調整，並停止收受港幣、歐元及人民幣匯入匯款，僅限收美元匯入匯款；匯出匯款辦理幣別仍維持美元、港幣、歐元及人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n中華郵政公司表示，配合美國紐約梅隆銀行為其美元存匯行，籲請民眾如有外匯匯入需求，請改以美元匯入，讓款項順利匯達，相關業務詳情請至中華郵政公司全球資訊網（http：//<a href=\"http://www.post.gov.tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.post.gov.tw&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPtToc6H19M6%2Bti4cloj%2BWDc%3D&h=e60652e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.post.gov.tw</a>）查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190626/1475683.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190626%2F1475683.htm&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPtToc6H19M6%2Bti4cloj%2BWDc%3D&h=f3d48dd9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190626/1475683.htm</a>"},{"pid":"cffb7cf22e81c134cd01eb223bf75131c8faf2f6","tid":1278419,"uid":75959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:59:56.000Z","msg":"反了反了"},{"pid":"f5b96ea38cbd25aff5a2c012cb07a7317b2a4fe7","tid":1278419,"uid":249473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:10:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}